  <br>
  <tt>svn co svn://svn.d-i.alioth.debian.org/svn/d-i/trunk debian-installer/installer/doc</tt>
  <li><a href="http://svn.debian.org/wsvn/d-i/trunk/installer/doc/manual/?rev=0&amp;sc=0">Interface web</a>
